<P>__{(to chewie)}
<D>__{why do you take this apart now? i'm trying to get us out of here and you pull both of these.}
<A>__{chewie grumbles in irritation.}
<C>__{threepio}
<D>__{excuse me, sir.}
<C>__{han}
<P>__{(to chewie)}
<D>__{put them back together right now.}
<C>__{threepio}
<D>__{might i have a word with you, please?}
