<D>__{i don't know where he is.}
<C>__{threepio}
<D>__{nobody knows where he is.}
<C>__{han}
<D>__{what do you mean, "nobody knows"?}
<A>__{han glances at the fading light at the entrance of the ice cave as night slowly begins to fall on the planet.}
<C>__{threepio}
<D>__{well, uh, you see...}
